Creating performant, maintainable custom controls in OpenMaui requires understanding the rendering pipeline and following established patterns. Here are battle-tested practices for building production-quality Skia-based controls.

## 1. Extend the Right Base Class

Choose your base class based on control complexity:

```csharp
// Simple controls with no children
public class CustomIndicator : SkiaView
{
